menu "breadboard: bb_queue"

config BB_QUEUE_REGISTRY_MAX
    int "Ring registry capacity (max concurrently-tracked bb_queue_t handles)"
    default 16
    range 1 32
    help
        Capacity of the diagnostic ring registry consumed by
        GET /api/diag/rings. Every bb_queue_create() self-registers here
        (best-effort); a full registry logs a warning and does not fail
        ring creation. Must be <= BB_REGISTRY_SNAPSHOT_MAX (64).

        Raising this increases the /api/diag/rings handler stack by
        ~44 bytes per entry.

endmenu
